Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…热死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办啊  这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早上电视里说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:10.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这是今年夏天最热的一个早晨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  这么热的话安娜就要融化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,…不会融化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有融化过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过融化之后是什么感觉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我不会融化了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,输了的人负责拿书包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我猜拳很弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:32.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,两个两个来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏的激情甲子园！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,两次中只要胜一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我先和这家伙玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:43.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,再比一次！再比一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,石头  剪子  布！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:53.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,谁输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好！石头  剪子  布！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们可真是残忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～回去了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的就不用了  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也自己来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:31.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已经说好的事情就一定要做到啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是为了什么才猜拳的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让别人背自己的书包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,然后轻松地去品尝那甜蜜的感觉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:46.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  等一下  我认为这很不公平…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好凉快啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  空调好伟大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒也一样的伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有东京体育馆的13倍的大小也很伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有空调的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是无法想象了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,恐龙是怎么生活的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,空调可真是好伟大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别耍我啊  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小美你在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  热死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一滴水就是一滴血啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一滴酒也是一滴血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,水…水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:25.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊  想喝水的话就直说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以喝！里面有毒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,给…给我水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,自己去倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  配合的真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是绿洲！看到绿洲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我们经历了40天之久的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,途中遭遇了沙暴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了骆驼和水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,连喜欢的电视节目都看不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴一个一个地死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,然后安娜融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,而现在  总算是看到绿洲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:30.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:41.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你一个人去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:46.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我不要  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事就交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的敌人就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,「那里」是指绿洲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是你真正的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:06:59.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是  配合得太差啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不…是因为你在一半换了个作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.81,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,(冰激凌)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,石头  剪子  布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:34.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,牙城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小千赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  荞麦面店吗？我要订餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是荞麦面店？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:51.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一份冰淇凌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还只点自己的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:55.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来是回转寿司店…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  恶作剧也要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:02.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你用的是我的手机啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗓子干了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,金戈尔是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？金戈尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,金青蛙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.66,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,（日语中「戈尔」和「青蛙」读音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说金子什么的  真是夸张的饮料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,G  I  N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:57.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:04.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,G  E  R  A  L  E
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,读作Ginger Ale啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上次承蒙你照顾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那里可是我的休憩之所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那个家庭餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  您说的是什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,您认错人了——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:39.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这么热你还这么有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:47.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷在家庭餐厅里认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但那个不是金青蛙  而是叫做Ginger Ale！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:53.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,凉凉君两个  Mild Dazs三个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:02.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一共是1176日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我开发票
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,您的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,请写松冈美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  手机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,忘在家里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:24.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呃  软弱的各位现代儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有因为吹空调太多而把嗓子搞坏啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始  进行嗓子的检查诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,（啊～我全身都发烫了～）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这样很对不起空调吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:05.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:10.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我热了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…我热了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一个是安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:21.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,用英语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎回来  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇凌呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在冰箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就要吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:12.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:16.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  还完全没睡醒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:27.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃冰淇凌？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还是过一会儿再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  把门关上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,会被烤熟！被煮熟！被点着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:38.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呼…好热…哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗！你是笨蛋吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你在做什么啊！真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要睡这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不要打我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是我的房间啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是我现在这里睡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了  先放在这里吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟这个没有关系吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了吵死了吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很吵的是小美才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  给我让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不讲理的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别把姐姐吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事都写在这个上面  （手机也调成静音模式）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,何必呢…到别的房间去不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是要在这间房里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,走廊里非常热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,佐竹把舌头都伸出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:04.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狗要伸出舌头来出汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,伸出舌头了  伸出舌头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不能说话好难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啊  因为是打喷嚏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger Ale和青蛙之间有什么关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:46.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想吵醒姐姐还是不想吵醒她？\N是哪个啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是想玩一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那么Ginger Ale里没有放青蛙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的「谜」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:08.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始进行耳朵的检查诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我热了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:31.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,（那一位的脑袋是不是坏了）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,检  检查耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天有好吃的冰淇凌  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是无法想象没有冰淇凌的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是  恐龙没有冰淇凌吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,又是怎样活下来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小千你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,恐龙的时代不可能有冰淇凌吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为空调吹多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是应该把温度稍微设高一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,180度20分钟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是烤蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然冰淇凌很好  蛋糕也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比如果冻的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢琼脂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,黑蜜的也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说到琼脂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是可爱得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你也别总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,说些让人听不懂的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你再好好看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要无视我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是感冒了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有做亏心事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就直接看着爸爸的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:37.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就踩着影子回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是踩到了没影子的地方就要负责拿书包
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,走喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,冲  冲啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:19.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:21.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是难点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:27.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:37.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去和姐姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:56.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:22:00.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:04.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:09.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我全身都发烫了～…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了的暑假！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  姐姐  好想要到哪里去玩一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  大家一起去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:49.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:50.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！去海边！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,…小美你拿着摄像机在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:54.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,自由研究
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:55.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！怎么回事？这不是我吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很有冲击性的画面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也有伸惠姐的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:04.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这  这家伙…把她埋在沙滩上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下回也要看棉花糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:11.00,biaoti1,,0000,0000,0000,,『海水浴』
